sourcesContent: $(document).ready(function(){$("*[data-theme]").click(function(e){e.preventDefault();var t,o,a=$(this).attr("data-theme");t="theme",o=a,"undefined"!=typeof Storage?localStorage.setItem(t,o):window.alert("Please use a modern browser to properly view this template!"),$("#theme").attr({href:"css/colors/"+a+".css"})});localStorage.getItem("theme");$("#themecolors").on("click","a",function(){$("#themecolors li a").removeClass("working"),$(this).addClass("working")})});
